Package: liblingmowindow1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lingmo Desktop - Application Window Base Library (runtime)
 Lingmo Window provides application window abstraction for the Lingmo
 Desktop environment, including CSD support, window effects, and
 platform window management.

Package: liblingmowindow-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: liblingmowindow1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         liblingmotheme-dev
Description: Lingmo Desktop - Application Window Base Library (development)
 This package contains headers and CMake integration for building
 applications that use Lingmo Window.

Package: qml6-module-lingmowindow
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: liblingmowindow1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         qml6-module-lingmotheme,
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lingmo Desktop - Application Window Base Library (QML module)
  This package contains QML bindings for the Lingmo Window library,
  providing Window, HeaderBar, Dialog, and WindowEffects QML types.
